    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This well-appointed model offers a refined driving experience, featuring a clean interior and a robust mechanical history. It represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver seeking quality without compromise. Inspection reveals a vehicle that has been cared for with diligence, ensuring it meets our rigorous standards for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new adventure! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and has been very well-loved. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring maximum traction out of corners. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe to maintain chassis integrity. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing the original MacPherson strut and multi-link rear setup for precise lateral load management. Cosmetically, the car shows well with minor patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle. Mechanically robust and ready for spirited weekend use.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Regular service history. Clean title. Reliable performance. Minor exterior wear.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances daily utility with a premium driving experience. The exterior paint still holds a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the trunk lid consistent with careful use. The factory alloy wheels are wrapped in tires with substantial tread remaining, though the front right wheel shows a light touch of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All interior technology\u2014including the premium audio system, navigation, and heated seats\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, this car is solid. It has been serviced at regular intervals, the engine runs quietly at idle, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. It has never been smoked in and has been garage-kept for the majority of its life. This is an honest, dependable car that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies the intersection of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional assessment to ensure mechanical standards remain high and aesthetic appeal is preserved. Featuring a robust powertrain and a refined interior, this vehicle offers a superior driving experience for the discerning motorist. We invite you to acquire this well-preserved example of automotive engineering, priced to reflect its solid standing in the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and I'd love for it to go to a great new home. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit showcases exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and remains thermally efficient under load. The double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of deflection in this chassis\u2014has been reinforced with plates for increased torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with precise synchronizer engagement, feeding a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, ensuring the communicative steering and neutral handling balance characteristic of the M-division. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
